Marketing Brief:
   Noted....
COMIC BOOKS: Several top comic-book artists are leaving
Marvel Entertainment Group to join Malibu Graphics Publishing
Group. The move, which was expected, shouldn't affect Marvel,
according to Donald Thompson, editor of Comics Buyer's Guide.
Marvel has about half of the $500 million comic-book market,
and Malibu has about 3%, according to Malibu.
